{"tid":1724002,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中大理大事件證明「大台」令人腐化！切戒！","createTime":"2019-11-15T10:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:14:53.000Z","uid":254452,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e73c76b85527adee3f68808d090d70b036fb8091","tid":1724002,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"收物資的人屌9送物資黎的人<br />\n開記者會爭話語權（我唔會話係鬼，純粹覺得想爭發言權）<br />\n<br />\n呢啲事就可以令大家互屌分化 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歸根究底就係「大台」呢個引誘作怪</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">人一有權力就好易變質</span></span></strong><br />\n大家支持中大理大 當中好易令人有虛榮感，覺得自己處於領導/話事位置，就開始屌人，命令人。<br />\n<br />\n絕非分化，只想提醒手足 ，任何時刻，都要提醒自己非大台，非領導，手足平等，先可互勉行到最後。"},{"pid":"c17c2f0e948aa2cc1d8afaceade4e792e8b99113","tid":1724002,"uid":254452,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:50:45.000Z","msg":"再簡單的一個例子 <br />\n一個普通人揸住個大聲公就好易覺得自己有權力 變左大台"},{"pid":"c35178f9982510315303ab7f8c43cd58beaa5058","tid":1724002,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"手足切記be humble"},{"pid":"569987558631deab8814496b9ac372b5c7580823","tid":1724002,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"Be water <br />\nBe humble"},{"pid":"42c1dc66b4ed215393a0278d3957ba3a07916e1f","tid":1724002,"uid":201703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02a4872f6ecc019f8d74d592b5485f5ff18d0cd5","tid":1724002,"uid":17209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:04:17.000Z","msg":"be humble"},{"pid":"9196009609e24ef7abbefb6a55e511b049e2d9dc","tid":1724002,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d38ae4af35f2f74b2873e62fa71fca85bd832189","tid":1724002,"uid":35211,"like":